name: Dogewhale
description: Dogewhale is a protocol with a deflationary token backed by multi-doge reserves. It contributes to various philanthropy causes and as a member of the Doge Alliance, it integrates gamified quests with the purpose of building up DeFi across crypto. The multi-doge reserve allows token holders to claim 10% of its value at pre-established checkpoints. Checkpoint 1 starts at $12500. In the last checkpoint, 100% of the value can be redeemed by holders.
